title: bookcase
tags:
---
<<declare $thelema to false>>
[nomarkup][Bookcase is filled with a myriad of items. Not only books, but it also nests big TV, radio, some vases… There are modern books on the shelves, but also several occult tomes line the wall, and the faint scent of lignin permeates the air. These books must be pretty old. There are also several scrolls. You don't know if they are made from paper or parchment. You even find a traditional quill that is gaining the dust in one of the shelf compartments. It's a weird fusion of new and old.][/nomarkup]
{$kieran}: Oh my… do you see these books?
<<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
    {$anastasia}: What, not alphabetized and color-coded, poindexter?
    [nomarkup][Kieran just rolls his eyes.][/nomarkup]
    {$kieran}: No? Just take a closer look, occult books lying next to normal, present day books. Popular literature.
    {$anastasia}: So what? She is your Sire's ghoul. It's obvious she's interested in that.
    {$kieran}: Not when you know her better. She never showed any interest in the magic and the occult. She was satisfied with running the show for Catherina.
<<endif>>
[nomarkup][Kieran leans towards the shelf looking at the titles more closely][/nomarkup]
{$kieran}: Some of these books seem out of place. Take a look, but don't touch anything just yet.
-> [nomarkup][Examine the books Kieran is interested with.][Intellicence + Occult][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseOccultRoll") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseOccultRoll>>
-> [nomarkup][Examine the normal books.][Intellicence + Academics][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseAcademicsRoll") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseAcademicsRoll>>
-> [nomarkup][Turn on the TV.][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseTV") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseTV>>
-> [nomarkup][Turn on the radio.][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseRadio") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseRadio>>
-> [nomarkup][Check what's behind TV.][Strength + Athletics][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseStrenghtRoll") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseStrenghtRoll>>
-> [nomarkup][Try to peek what's on the top of the shelf.][Dexterity + Athletics][/nomarkup] <<if visited("bookcaseDexterityRoll") == false>>
    <<jump bookcaseDexterityRoll>>
-> [nomarkup][Step back.][/nomarkup]
===
